<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@100;200;300;400;500;600&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Emerging Africa Email</title>
    <style>
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .wrapper {
                width: 100% !important;
            }
            .container{
                margin: 2% !important;
            }
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #f1f1f1;
            min-height: 900px;
        }

        .container {
            margin-left: 10%;
            margin-right: 10%;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 5%;
            padding: 5%;
        }

        .logo-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 64px;
            background: #F57921;
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 5px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
        }

        h3 {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 24px;
            line-height: 120%;
            /* identical to box height, or 29px */

            text-align: center;

            color: #333333;

        }

        p.text {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 150%;
            /* or 21px */

            text-align: center;

            color: #666666;

        }

        .code-box {
            width: 64px !important;
            height: 64px !important;
            border-radius: 100%;
            background: #FFF6F5;
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 39px;
            line-height: 47px;
            /* display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center; */

            /* Disabled Colour */

            color: #B3B3B3;

        }

        p.footer-text {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 10px;
            line-height: 150%;
            /* or 15px */

            text-align: center;

            color: #666666;

        }

        .footer-link a {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 100%;
            /* identical to box height, or 12px */

            text-align: center;
            text-decoration-line: underline;

            color: #666666;
            padding-right: 15px;
            padding-left: 15px;

        }

        .footer-link a:not(:last-child) {
            border-right: 1px solid #C4C4C4;
        }

        .button {
            background: #F57921;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 203px;
            height: 56px;
            font-family: 'Open Sans', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 100%;
            /* identical to box height, or 16px */


            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="logo-wrapper">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/0BHZKjk/logo-white.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <img src="https://i.ibb.co/sVZgLJg/otp-verify.png" alt="">
             <h3>Welcome, let’s start building wealth</h3>

            <p class="text">Hi {{name}}, welcome to Emerging Africa Trustees. In order to get started, you can now <br> start
                building and managing wealth on the go.</p>
            

            <p class="text" style="margin-top: 20px;"> Kindly click the button below to activate your account.</p>

            <a href="#">


                    <button style="margin-top: 10px;"  class="button">Activate Account</button>
                </a>
          
            <p class="text" style="margin-top: 20px;">If you are having any issues with your account, please don’t
                hesitate to <br>contact us by replying to this email.</p>

        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 50px; text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://facebook.com/" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 10px;"
                    src="https://i.ibb.co/NjrrNJj/facebook.png" alt="facebook" border="0"></a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 10px;"
                    src="https://i.ibb.co/Vwyj46C/instagram.png" alt="instagram" border="0"></a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 10px;"
                    src="https://i.ibb.co/wZmHvND/linkedin.png" alt="linkedin" border="0"></a>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/" target="_blank"><img style="margin-right: 10px;"
                    src="https://i.ibb.co/3kXNJtz/twitter.png" alt="twitter" border="0"></a>
            <p class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 50px;">Copyright © 2022 Emerging Africa Group. All Rights
                Reserved. If<br> you wish to stop
                receiving this mail, click <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #666666" href="#">here</a> to unsubscribe
            </p>

            <div class="footer-link" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="https://emerging-wealth.netlify.app/auth/login">Website </a> <a
                    href="https://emerging-wealth.netlify.app/auth/login">FAQ</a> <a
                    href="https://emerging-wealth.netlify.app/auth/login">Privacy policy</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

